Author: paperklipp
Text: I know that things feels like they’re spiralling out of control right now but YOU are stronger than the chaos and you can find your way back.   It seems from what you’ve said that you sort of feel like reality is flipping the script on you; things used to make sense and now they don’t anymore, things that used to work don’t work anymore. EDs being centred on control, this must feel pretty catastrophic. But everything that’s changing is internal to you, and you have the power to get on top of it, just give yourself some slack and some space to get centred. Lay out a plan, and then stick to it, instead of just trying to work blindly towards a goal.   It will be okay.
